# Research Result

**Goal:** Prove: every 6-dimensional subspace of F_p⁹ contains a nonzero vector with all coordinates in {0,...,p-1} and coordinate sum at most p.

This is the upper bound for η(C_p³) = 8(p-1)+1. The lower bound is already machine-checked. This one theorem completes the picture.

Do not search. Do not enumerate. Prove.
